{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"真的，以月亮盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"以逝去的黑夜盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"以显照的黎明盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"火狱确是一个大难，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"可以警告人类，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"警告你们中欲前进者或欲后退者；"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"各人将因自己的营谋而作抵押，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"惟幸福的人们除外。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"他们在乐园中互相询问，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"问犯罪人们的情状，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"你们为什么堕入火狱呢？ ”"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"他们说：“我们没有礼拜，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"也没有济贫，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"我们与妄言的人们一道妄言，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"我们否认报应日，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"一直到死亡降临了我们。”"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"说情者的说情，将无益于他们。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"他们怎么退避这教训呢？"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"他们好像一群惊慌的驴子，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"刚逃避了一只狮子一样。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"不然，他们中的每个人都希望获得一些展开的天经。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"绝不然，他们不畏惧后世！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"真的，这《古兰经》确是一个教诲！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"谁愿意，谁记忆它，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":56,"Text":"他们只因安拉的意欲而记忆它。他是应受敬畏的，他是宜于赦宥的。"}]}